headline.main: DC United Ties Sporting Kansas City 0-0 in Last RFK Opener
headline.print_headline: DC United Ties Sporting Kansas City 0-0 in Last RFK Opener

lead_paragraph: Bill Hamid made five saves, including one late against Dom Dwyer, to help D.C. United tie Sporting Kansas City 0-0 on Saturday night in team's last Major League Soccer home opener at RFK Stadium.
